{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"082ea0aada","title":"关于印发刘晓给中央电报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"297ce5eef9","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"082ea0aada"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"7746a9f755","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘晓，当时任中国驻苏联大使。12]小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记。"},{"id":"ae40fe56ad","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指刘晓1958年8月16日给中共中央的电报。电报说：不久前我曾往访库西宁同志，向他转告了毛主席对苏共中央关于王明情况通知的答复。他表示对毛主席能充分地理解苏共中央非常高兴，至于王明是否应该在苏继续治疗的问题，应完全由中共中央决定。既然毛主席认为他可以留下，这对苏方来说也不会成为负担。然后我向库西宁表示，毛主席很高兴地欢迎他在任何他认为方便的时间到中国做客，他表示非常感动。这个电报作为北戴河中共中央政治局扩大会议文件在会上印发。"}],"contents":[{"id":"863049f801","type":"title","text":"关于印发刘晓\"给中央电报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada"},{"id":"7746a9f755","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada"},{"id":"ae40fe56ad","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请印发会议客同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada"},{"id":"98102e414b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada"},{"id":"b18075bbf2","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada"}],"page":{"id":"f764909ec3","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"082ea0aada","start":77,"end":77}}}},"__N_SSG":true}